0.21.name: wordpress/tng-wordpress-plugin
0.21.description:
The Next Generation is a powerful PHP/MySQL script that acts as a central repository for all your genealogy research, and allows others to view and search through your records. This plugin integrates TNG with your Wordpress site. This plugin is free, but to use it you need to purchase TNG (currently $30).

NOTE#### If you are successfully using this plug in DO NOT upgrade to the version linked to this ReadMe file - it is NOT a newer version than what you have. Roger is trying to become familiar with publishing through the WordPress Plugins repository. This ReadMe will be updated and this note removed when the current version is available to install automatically.

Features

  1. Displays TNG within Wordpress with no iFrames (great for SEO!), on whichever page you choose.
  2. Requires no mods, and overwrites no core files. Just upload the plugin to your Wordpress plugins folder.
